  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 1.8em; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/09/17/936262f4c1164a0bab5c9db93caeb585.jpg\" style=\"height: 261px; font-family: verdana, 'lucida sans regular', 'lucida sans unicode', arial, sans-serif; width: 500px; color: rgb(34,34,34); line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThis week's topic: Sleep Deprivation (90-110 words)<br />\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) Share your story of sleep <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/deprivation\" target=\"_blank\">deprivation</a><br />\n\t2) Are you suffering from sleep deprivation? For what?<br />\n\t3) What methods do you recommend to avoid sleep deprivation?<br />\n\t4) Anything you would like to write</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAt some point, sleep deprivation turns to be the latest prevalence, which is notoriously called the &ldquo;new smoking&rdquo;. There is no exaggeration that we, in the modern society, pride for work overtime on little sleep. Even Margaret Thatcher, UK former Prime Minister, used to claim that she could work effectively on only four hours sleep a night. However, she was captured though archive video footage snoozing during the day. Undoubtedly, restful sleep is critical to high levels of performance. Under no circumstance should we trade sleep for work, not to mention for entertainment. Have a sound sleep from today.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169491293962/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827499/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827499\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p823203/\">如何把兴趣爱好变成钱？来让行家手把手教你</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p839767/\">2017雅思考试时间表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p828581/\">双语美文：整个世界因你而不同</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p828475/\">外国人最喜欢看的竟然是这些书</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767739/\">段子手的自白：我是如何从421进化到515的！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p790569/\">你肯定不会用英语打电话！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p843182/\">中老年自拍照：外国大叔大妈比90后还潮！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p823296/\">净化室内空气 选这些植物就对了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p592946/\">推荐！口语入门的经典教材</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761887/\">不识泰山！看着像乱涂乱画 一幅幅都贵成天价</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" targ